<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>592</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ qiú nǐ rán shāo zhōng guó xīn rán shāo zhōng guó xīn
 kàn nǐ zài zhōng guó de jiào huì kàn yī kàn nǐ de pū rén
 tā men shí zài guò duō de chéng shòu dǎ jī jīng shòu zhe fēng yǔ de xǐ lǐ
 dàn tā men cóng lái jiù bù wèi jù shì nà yàng de jiān dìng bù yí
 jiāo lǜ hé chǎng de huāng liáng hái yǒu nèi wài de yā lì
 zǒu nán chuǎng běi zài fēng chén pū pū lǐ méi yǒu tíng liú zhī de
 zhǔ rú guǒ zhè shì nǐ de zhǐ yì wǒ men huān xǐ gǎn xiè zàn měi nǐ
 nǎ pà tóu shàng shì wū yún jiǎo xià shì jīng jí yě yào bǎ fú yīn chuán dào de jí</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ qiú nǐ rán shāo zhōng guó xīn 迦南592</title>
</song>